item.title: San Francisco - 1
item.description: Larger and Hillier than I thought Yeah, this is a little bit late (~6 months after? I mean, I totally started this the day after I got back, but y’know). Still, to be entirely honest, stepping into San Francisco was a bit surreal. The busy streets were way too steep, and I felt as if I tripped on one of them, then I would go rolling down for miles with only a few trucks to stop me.
